25 Division I of this article apply in the county without exception or variation:
26 (1) § 2–201 (“Issuance by Comptroller”);
27 (2) [§ 2–202 (“Class 1 distillery license”);
28 (3)] § 2–203 (“Class 9 limited distillery license”);

